description: ***Please note that at this stage, you're registering your interest in this event only. We will contact you on 26th June to confirm your ticket and pass along details of the day*** Do you want to help #BuildTheBBC?   BBC Design + Engineering is...

values.value:
BBC Design + Engineering is hosting a networking and recruitment evening for all engineers, innovators, analysts, product people and anyone aspiring to be in the world of technology. From beginner level to managers and all the way to guru-level, we'd love to tell you about all of the exciting things we're doing in our near 100-year-old technology company. 

Please contact Darren Read (Darren.read@bbc.co.uk) for more information. 

Please register your interest to attend. Due to limited availability tickets will be issued by invitation only: https://lnkd.in/gWWs-XE

title: Do you want to help #BuildTheBBC? - An evening of tech talks, networking and pizza!
